<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/assets/about.jpg"
        alt="Our experts working together"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Our mission</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-base text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 sm:text-lg">
              At Glu Consult, we believe that technology should bring people and ideas together.
              Founded with a vision to create meaningful digital experiences, we’re a development
              agency dedicated to crafting high-quality software, user-centered designs, and
              innovative AI solutions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 sm:text-lg">
              Our team combines technical expertise with creativity, offering comprehensive services
              in Software Development, UI/UX Design, and AI Development and Testing. From
              custom-built software applications to intuitive interfaces, we work closely with our
              clients to understand their needs and bring their vision to life with precision and
              care.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 sm:text-lg">
              With Glu Consult, you're not just getting a service provider; you're gaining a partner
              who’s committed to your success. Let’s build something extraordinary together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
